                        <head>345. Editorial Note</head>
                        <p>On September 5, President <persName corresp="#p_EDD1">Eisenhower</persName> approved <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss>
                            5612/1, “U.S. Policy in Mainland Southeast Asia.” A partially
                            declassified text is printed in <hi rend="italic">United States–Vietnam
                                Relations, 1945–1967</hi>, Book 10, pages 1082–1095.</p>
